![# Brief Overview](https://cdn.modrinth.com/data/cached_images/a3995d545b7a77db2b2e994e67f2199c5030f8dc_0.webp)

Apel stands for **A**nimative **P**article **E**ngine **L**ibrary. Its goal is to give the developer a huge productivity boost by incorporating a powerful animation engine that allows for the management of complex particle animations. Thus the library aims to provide:

![# Why Use APEL?](https://cdn.modrinth.com/data/cached_images/304bf6cb01287cad79fb327400ce6bb0987ee934_0.webp)
To put it simply. APEL allows you to fully make these animations with **very few lines of code**:

